        <title>Hugo &#43; Stack 简单搭建一个静态博客</title>
        <link>https://example.com/p/hugo--stack-%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
